1
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:41,100
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 25]

3
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,350
Hello, Mr. Tan.

4
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,479
We meet again.

5
00:01:59,509 --> 00:02:00,200
Mr. Ji.

6
00:02:00,510 --> 00:02:01,400
I'm really sorry

7
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,280
to disturb you during work hours.

8
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:02,870
Not at all.

9
00:02:02,870 --> 00:02:03,310
Please sit.

10
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:03,640
Okay.

11
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:09,830
Actually, I came here today on purpose

12
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:11,360
because of something

13
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,690
related to me yesterday

14
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:15,000
that might drag Miss Xu Miyu

15
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,530
into unnecessary trouble.

16
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:18,890
Ms. Xu is a very important friend of mine.

17
00:02:18,890 --> 00:02:21,310
So I came to clear things up for her.

18
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,150
Mr. Tan, you're willing to go
to great lengths for a friend.

19
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:28,410
I can understand that.

20
00:02:28,430 --> 00:02:29,360
Rest assured.

21
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,400
According to the hotel's regulations,

22
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,800
if she didn't break any rules,

23
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,150
we absolutely won't wrong her.

24
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:33,840
Okay.

25
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:37,240
But it's a fact that she caused
a negative impact on the hotel.

26
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:39,270
We can only do things by the book.

27
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:41,170
Then I'll make it short.

28
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:44,360
I didn't stay in Room 1219 yesterday.

29
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,800
After I settled Ms. Xu down,

30
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,310
I went to Room 1810.

31
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,120
I slept on the sofa
in the living room in my father's suite

32
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,200
for the whole night.

33
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:54,130
Of course, this is
the best solution I could think of.

34
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:56,960
Then, Mr. Tan, have you ever thought

35
00:02:57,910 --> 00:02:59,400
that if you didn't interfere,

36
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,170
things wouldn't be so complicated?

37
00:03:01,170 --> 00:03:05,350
[Purong Hotel]

38
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:07,080
Mr. Ji, you think I'm being a busybody,

39
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,710
don't you?

40
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:10,260
Mr. Tan, you've misunderstood.

41
00:03:11,010 --> 00:03:12,050
What I mean is,

42
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,680
you are also a public figure.

43
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,829
You should know better than us

44
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:18,310
how to avoid gossip.

45
00:03:19,290 --> 00:03:21,040
A hotel is full of gossip.

46
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,520
This kind of rumor

47
00:03:22,790 --> 00:03:24,910
can be a fatal blow to someone.

48
00:03:25,130 --> 00:03:27,130
If you were there at the time, Mr. Ji,

49
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:29,260
seeing Ms. Xu being
humiliated by her family

50
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:30,870
and mocked by her colleagues,

51
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:31,890
would you just stand by and do nothing?

52
00:03:31,890 --> 00:03:33,200
But I would never
take advantage of her vulnerability.

53
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,040
What do you think,

54
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,850
Mr. Tan?

55
00:03:37,570 --> 00:03:39,829
Mr. Ji, may I ask you
a question in return?

56
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:41,430
In what capacity

57
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:42,590
are you saying these things to me?

58
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:43,980
And in what capacity

59
00:03:44,010 --> 00:03:46,540
are you approaching
an employee of our hotel?

60
00:03:56,110 --> 00:03:58,210
Mr. Ji, I think you've missed the point.

61
00:03:58,210 --> 00:03:59,960
Actually, what you should care about

62
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,220
is why she got so drunk,

63
00:04:01,930 --> 00:04:03,710
what exactly she's been through,

64
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:04,470
and how much she's endured

65
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:06,120
that she shouldn't have.

66
00:04:06,140 --> 00:04:07,820
Don't focus on me.

67
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,630
What do you think?

68
00:04:18,269 --> 00:04:19,709
Mr. Ji, I believe that

69
00:04:19,750 --> 00:04:21,450
for employees as precious as gold,

70
00:04:21,450 --> 00:04:23,980
just providing a shining stage
isn't enough.

71
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:26,200
You must also be there
for them in their vulnerable moments.

72
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:28,400
Of course, you have
a good eye for talent, Mr. Ji.

73
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,460
You must understand this principle.

74
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,120
I've also checked the surveillance.

75
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,780
Indeed,

76
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,630
Tan Jizhou stayed in room 1219

77
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:41,490
for less than 5 minutes
before coming out.

78
00:04:41,490 --> 00:04:42,310
Two minutes later,

79
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:45,030
he appeared in the corridor
of the executive floor.

80
00:04:45,030 --> 00:04:46,070
He wasn't seen on camera again

81
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:47,190
until around 8:40

82
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:49,270
the next morning.

83
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,630
I indirectly asked Mr. Tan Sr. about it.

84
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:53,480
It's true...

85
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:00,670
Hello, Mr. Ji.

86
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,600
Hello, Mr. Xue.

87
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,040
What are you whispering about?

88
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:03,920
Nothing.

89
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:04,770
Sorry, Mr. Ji.

90
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,240
Bro,

91
00:05:09,590 --> 00:05:11,230
are you out of your mind?

92
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:12,920
You want to be a tyrant?

93
00:05:15,930 --> 00:05:16,760
This way.

94
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:24,950
Okay.

95
00:05:24,950 --> 00:05:25,830
Here.

96
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,040
Xiaoyan.

97
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:30,310
Do you think our complaint

98
00:05:30,340 --> 00:05:31,950
will backfire?

99
00:05:32,190 --> 00:05:34,140
Look at her, acting like nothing happened

100
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:36,090
after coming out of Mr. Ji's office.

101
00:05:36,090 --> 00:05:38,970
Xu Miyu staying in
a guest's room late at night

102
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,560
is an undeniable fact.

103
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:42,790
We have it all recorded in the computer.

104
00:05:43,370 --> 00:05:44,159
But that doesn't mean

105
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,760
they actually did anything.

106
00:05:45,770 --> 00:05:46,630
It doesn't matter.

107
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,670
Giving people cause
for gossip is unacceptable.

108
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:50,190
How can a lobby manager

109
00:05:50,210 --> 00:05:51,659
be so frivolous?

110
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,000
If word gets out,

111
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,750
it'll ruin our hotel's image.

112
00:05:55,330 --> 00:05:57,820
You guys really don't get it.

113
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:00,070
No.

114
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:02,730
I have to go talk
to Director Bai again later.

115
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:03,510
After all this,

116
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:04,630
we still can't bring her down.

117
00:06:04,630 --> 00:06:05,830
Is there no justice?

118
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:08,750
Come in.

119
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:12,310
Mr. Ji,

120
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:13,580
Director Bai is here.

121
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:14,430
Show him in.

122
00:06:16,770 --> 00:06:18,620
Mr. Ji, you were looking for me?

123
00:06:18,650 --> 00:06:19,450
Director Bai.

124
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,360
I heard you're very anxious to know

125
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:26,420
the investigation results of Ms. Xu
staying overnight in the guest room.

126
00:06:26,710 --> 00:06:27,950
Not really.

127
00:06:27,970 --> 00:06:30,030
They're just rumors among the staff.

128
00:06:31,250 --> 00:06:33,450
The matter has been
thoroughly investigated.

129
00:06:33,450 --> 00:06:35,300
Ms. Xu is not involved in any violations.

130
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:37,760
There will be no administrative penalties.

131
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:39,180
No punishment at all?

132
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:42,320
Mr. Ji, you might not
have heard the rumors.

133
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:45,180
It's said the scene was extremely indecent

134
00:06:45,210 --> 00:06:46,250
and unsightly.

135
00:06:46,550 --> 00:06:48,640
Did you see it with your own eyes?

136
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:49,340
No.

137
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:52,040
But the rumor is all over the place today.

138
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:54,440
Everyone is saying
that the lobby manager of our Front Office

139
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:56,880
got drunk and stayed in a guest's room.

140
00:06:57,110 --> 00:06:58,210
This has a very negative impact.

141
00:06:58,210 --> 00:07:00,970
I'm mainly afraid that the young girls
in the Front Office

142
00:07:00,970 --> 00:07:01,950
will follow her example.

143
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:03,950
It will be hard to manage them later.

144
00:07:03,970 --> 00:07:05,060
Didn't you just say

145
00:07:05,090 --> 00:07:07,620
that the subordinates
love to spread rumors?

146
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,530
That is indeed the case.

147
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,210
A wise man does not believe rumors.

148
00:07:11,210 --> 00:07:12,010
Director Bai.

149
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:14,560
Your department's employees
complained to you.

150
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,560
What investigations have you done?

151
00:07:16,770 --> 00:07:18,260
I haven't yet...

152
00:07:18,290 --> 00:07:20,750
Have you checked the hotel's surveillance?

153
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:21,310
No.

154
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:22,730
Have you asked the person involved?

155
00:07:22,730 --> 00:07:23,460
No.

156
00:07:23,490 --> 00:07:25,690
Spreading rumors without evidence

157
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,800
is a clear violation of hotel rules.

158
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:28,480
Also,

159
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,890
this complaint letter of yours

160
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:34,630
states that Xu Miyu spent the night
with a guest in his room.

161
00:07:34,770 --> 00:07:36,570
It's written in black and white.

162
00:07:36,790 --> 00:07:39,450
If we look into it
and it doesn't match the facts,

163
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:41,909
every single person who signed this

164
00:07:41,930 --> 00:07:43,770
will have to bear legal responsibility.

165
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:45,290
What is this?

166
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:48,520
These people do things without thinking.

167
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:50,040
Without any evidence,

168
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,040
and without reporting to their superiors,

169
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,500
they came straight to you.

170
00:07:53,490 --> 00:07:54,430
Seriously.

171
00:07:56,250 --> 00:07:58,780
So you were kept
in the dark too, Director Bai?

172
00:07:58,790 --> 00:08:00,810
Yes, I was misled by them.

173
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:01,790
Mr. Ji.

174
00:08:02,050 --> 00:08:03,920
Since you've investigated clearly,

175
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:06,080
and Ms. Xu was indeed wronged,

176
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:07,960
I'll go back
and give them a good talking-to.

177
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,430
Director Bai, if you can't handle it,

178
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:10,960
you can leave it to us.

179
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,450
I... I can handle it.

180
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:15,290
You don't need to
step in for such a small matter.

181
00:08:15,290 --> 00:08:16,440
Rest assured, Mr. Ji.

182
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,680
I know what to do.

183
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:18,580
I promise

184
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,360
that today's rumors

185
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,290
will turn into a gust of wind

186
00:08:22,290 --> 00:08:23,410
and blow far away.

187
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:26,640
Then I'll trouble you to take the lead

188
00:08:26,660 --> 00:08:28,320
and set a good example
for the Front Office.

189
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,560
Yes, yes, Mr. Ji.

190
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,630
Lu Xiaoyan,

191
00:08:40,929 --> 00:08:42,570
have you finished your situation report?

192
00:08:42,570 --> 00:08:43,210
No.

193
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,440
Why not?

194
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,860
You haven't even cleaned up your own mess,

195
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:49,980
and you're asking me about my report?

196
00:08:50,100 --> 00:08:51,050
Who do you think you are?

197
00:08:51,050 --> 00:08:52,360
I'm your boss,

198
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:54,110
and you made a mistake at work.

199
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,400
My superior will handle my problems.

200
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:01,480
Please give me the report now.

201
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:02,380
I won't.

202
00:09:03,050 --> 00:09:04,850
What are you going to do about it?

203
00:09:05,420 --> 00:09:06,130
Do you want to know?

204
00:09:06,130 --> 00:09:06,960
Yes.

205
00:09:09,070 --> 00:09:09,760
Ying.

206
00:09:10,050 --> 00:09:11,280
Give me the performance appraisal form.

207
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:12,160
Okay, Ma'am.

208
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:19,200
I've deducted 20 points
from your monthly performance.

209
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,320
If you don't submit it tomorrow,

210
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,580
I'll deduct 30 points.

211
00:09:21,860 --> 00:09:22,620
You...

212
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:24,770
Director Bai!

213
00:09:25,020 --> 00:09:25,630
Director Bai,

214
00:09:25,630 --> 00:09:27,440
please come and judge for us!

215
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:29,320
Director Bai.

216
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:30,960
Ms. Xu.

217
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:31,850
It's lunch break.

218
00:09:31,850 --> 00:09:32,970
Haven't you gone to eat?

219
00:09:32,970 --> 00:09:34,950
I'll go after I handle this.

220
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,930
Director Bai, look at Ms. Xu.

221
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,080
She is crazy today.

222
00:09:38,150 --> 00:09:39,270
Her own behavior is improper,

223
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:40,750
yet she deducts 20 points from me.

224
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:42,530
Will you leaders do something about it?

225
00:09:42,530 --> 00:09:43,840
And with so many of us

226
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,700
signing the complaint letter,

227
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:47,980
will the general manager even read it?

228
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,270
You little girls,

229
00:09:49,270 --> 00:09:51,530
I haven't settled the score with you yet.

230
00:09:51,580 --> 00:09:53,890
What complaint letter?

231
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,750
What nonsense are you all making?

232
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:57,150
Whatever Ms. Xu does

233
00:09:57,150 --> 00:09:58,520
is none of your business.

234
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,780
As for you, Lu Xiaoyan,

235
00:09:59,930 --> 00:10:02,300
I haven't punished you for yesterday.

236
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:04,890
Get your self-criticism written now.

237
00:10:04,890 --> 00:10:05,960
Write down the whole process

238
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,800
clearly and seriously.

239
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:09,620
Hand it in today once you finish.

240
00:10:13,470 --> 00:10:15,400
She should hand it in to you, right?

241
00:10:16,370 --> 00:10:17,830
Let Ms. Xu review it.

242
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:19,170
If you don't finish it today,

243
00:10:19,170 --> 00:10:20,770
don't come to work tomorrow.

244
00:10:21,230 --> 00:10:22,110
Did you hear me?

245
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:24,040
All of you,

246
00:10:24,070 --> 00:10:25,710
starting today,

247
00:10:25,740 --> 00:10:28,970
if anyone thinks
they are smart and talks nonsense,

248
00:10:28,990 --> 00:10:30,470
or passes notes,

249
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:31,760
I'm warning you,

250
00:10:32,100 --> 00:10:33,620
I won't protect you.

251
00:10:37,630 --> 00:10:39,630
Ms. Xu, go have lunch.

252
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,410
When she finishes the self-criticism,

253
00:10:41,410 --> 00:10:42,540
have her come to you.

254
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:44,270
It has to pass your approval.

255
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,740
If you are not satisfied,

256
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:46,870
make her rewrite it.

257
00:10:47,190 --> 00:10:48,560
Thank you, Director Bai.

258
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:50,310
Thank you for your support.

259
00:10:50,340 --> 00:10:51,390
It's my duty.

260
00:10:51,530 --> 00:10:52,560
I'll go eat now.

261
00:10:59,150 --> 00:11:00,480
Director Bai.

262
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:01,120
She...

263
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,310
Don't point.

264
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:04,080
Hurry up and write.

265
00:11:05,750 --> 00:11:07,480
A bunch of troublesome girls.

266
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:15,750
Mr. Ji.

267
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:16,920
Morning.

268
00:11:38,550 --> 00:11:40,070
I recently discovered

269
00:11:40,090 --> 00:11:42,570
life is just a series of disappointments.

270
00:11:44,270 --> 00:11:45,950
What do you think of this?

271
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:48,360
This is so impressive.

272
00:11:49,070 --> 00:11:51,870
I actually really want to transfer Ya
to the Western restaurant.

273
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:54,270
But look at Bao's skills.

274
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:55,730
She really can't compare.

275
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:57,510
Ya's knife skills are excellent.

276
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:59,270
Isn't it good for her
to be in the Chinese restaurant?

277
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:00,390
She doesn't like it.

278
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:01,790
She just wants to make cakes.

279
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:04,050
Things just don't go as planned, do they?

280
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,720
Did you make this?

281
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,510
I just made it for fun.

282
00:12:10,810 --> 00:12:12,420
Let me steam it.

283
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:17,380
What about Ya?

284
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:19,150
Ya?

285
00:12:19,670 --> 00:12:21,670
I can only tell her
to let nature take its course,

286
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:24,190
and keep working with me
at the Chinese restaurant.

287
00:12:24,190 --> 00:12:26,070
You should also let things be.

288
00:12:26,090 --> 00:12:28,030
There are many things
you simply can't control.

289
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:29,790
As for those baseless rumors,

290
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,290
just ignore them.

291
00:12:31,310 --> 00:12:33,010
What's the worst that could happen?

292
00:12:33,010 --> 00:12:35,450
At most, it reaches Mr. Ji's office.

293
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:37,280
Mr. Ji will swat them

294
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:38,450
all like flies.

295
00:12:40,950 --> 00:12:43,060
They've sent me
this joint compliant letter.

296
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:44,270
Of course, I could

297
00:12:44,830 --> 00:12:45,840
suppress it

298
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:48,550
and keep you in your position
against broad objection.

299
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:49,900
But why should I do that?

300
00:12:50,980 --> 00:12:51,910
Are you worth it?

301
00:12:56,290 --> 00:12:58,040
Did he bully you again?

302
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:01,290
He is the general manager.

303
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:03,410
There is really nothing between us.

304
00:13:03,430 --> 00:13:05,030
Stop always trying

305
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:06,770
to pair us up.

306
00:13:07,790 --> 00:13:08,670
Okay.

307
00:13:08,670 --> 00:13:09,750
I'll stop talking.

308
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:12,680
Then don't look so sad.

309
00:13:12,870 --> 00:13:13,670
Smile a little.

310
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:15,030
Cheer up, okay?

311
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,030
That looks terrible.

312
00:13:23,270 --> 00:13:25,330
You know how to make corn out of dough?

313
00:13:28,010 --> 00:13:29,360
What else can you make?

314
00:13:29,390 --> 00:13:31,120
I can also make little monkeys.

315
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:32,750
Wait.

316
00:13:45,250 --> 00:13:46,710
They are all a bit lacking.

317
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:49,180
Kuanli has been interfering,

318
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:50,610
making it hard to find

319
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:53,360
good pastry chefs in this city.

320
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:55,440
We've made appointments with so many

321
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,550
foreign Michelin chefs.

322
00:13:56,550 --> 00:13:57,680
You've met them all,

323
00:13:57,800 --> 00:13:59,390
but you're not satisfied with any of them.

324
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:01,510
We can't just look at titles and sales.

325
00:14:01,510 --> 00:14:02,270
Most importantly,

326
00:14:02,270 --> 00:14:03,750
they have to match the style

327
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:05,480
and character of Purong Hotel.

328
00:14:05,510 --> 00:14:07,630
Just like that Yan Du Xian from before.

329
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:09,120
As for the style of Purong Hotel,

330
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,910
it's the old Shanghai flavor.

331
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:14,760
For example, the almond pastries

332
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,150
and eclairs from Harbin Food Factory,

333
00:14:16,150 --> 00:14:18,170
and the palmiers from Park Hotel.

334
00:14:18,190 --> 00:14:20,430
That field is way too competitive.

335
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:24,150
Should we offer
Chinese-style afternoon tea?

336
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:26,480
Chinese-style afternoon tea?

337
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:27,360
Look.

338
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:29,720
Think about how many milk tea brands

339
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,390
are moving into Chinese tea now.

340
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:32,790
The lines for Shen Dacheng's Qingtuan

341
00:14:32,790 --> 00:14:34,390
and Laodafang's Suzhou-style mooncakes

342
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:35,870
are so long.

343
00:14:35,890 --> 00:14:36,630
That's enough to show

344
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:39,840
that the market for Chinese pastries
is not to be underestimated.

345
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:41,320
Besides, our Chinese restaurant

346
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,750
is currently trending.

347
00:14:42,870 --> 00:14:45,510
Rather than crowding
into the Western dessert market,

348
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,370
we might as well

349
00:14:46,630 --> 00:14:48,030
use Chinese tea snacks

350
00:14:48,050 --> 00:14:49,530
to make a breakthrough.

351
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,440
Come help.

352
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:14,720
Mr. Bao.

353
00:15:14,740 --> 00:15:16,340
Please introduce this to us.

354
00:15:18,580 --> 00:15:19,930
This half is Chinese-style.

355
00:15:19,930 --> 00:15:21,530
That half is Western-style.

356
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,480
Mr. Ji. Mr. Guo.

357
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,750
Mr. Xue. This apprentice of mine

358
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:31,520
is clumsy with words. He knows how to do
the job, just not how to explain it.

359
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:33,180
Like these today,

360
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:35,600
we have both Chinese and Western styles.

361
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:38,000
Mr. Bao's concept is
to embrace a mix of cultures.

362
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,200
It centers on Chinese desserts,

363
00:15:40,270 --> 00:15:42,120
paired with Italian, Japanese,

364
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,240
and British classics,

365
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:46,760
to create
a cultural exchange on the plate.

366
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:52,630
As for the Chinese desserts,

367
00:15:52,670 --> 00:15:54,600
are there any other new creations?

368
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,450
Take a look at this,

369
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,600
the Rainbow Mille-Feuille.

370
00:16:02,290 --> 00:16:03,650
This looks good.

371
00:16:04,780 --> 00:16:05,610
Let me try it.

372
00:16:11,170 --> 00:16:12,100
It's delicious.

373
00:16:13,630 --> 00:16:14,480
However,

374
00:16:14,870 --> 00:16:15,960
Xinlong Hotel

375
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:18,620
is also making
the Four Seasons Mille-Feuille.

376
00:16:18,630 --> 00:16:20,000
If we make it too,

377
00:16:21,170 --> 00:16:22,770
it would be too competitive.

378
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,670
But of course,

379
00:16:24,670 --> 00:16:26,000
if there are no other options,

380
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,630
we can try this first.

381
00:16:27,920 --> 00:16:29,120
Wait a minute, Mr. Ji.

382
00:16:29,730 --> 00:16:31,280
I have a hidden item here.

383
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:34,430
What secret weapon are you hiding?

384
00:16:34,430 --> 00:16:35,280
Bring it out.

385
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:36,260
You said it.

386
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:50,720
Very good.

387
00:16:51,630 --> 00:16:52,630
Who made this?

388
00:16:54,510 --> 00:16:55,790
Xu Miyu.

389
00:17:03,260 --> 00:17:04,410
Okay, are you ready?

390
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,200
Ready.

391
00:17:07,089 --> 00:17:08,880
Okay, change your pose for another one.

392
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,609
Fix your hair. It's a bit messy.

393
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:13,900
[Mom]

394
00:17:16,369 --> 00:17:17,329
Here we go.

395
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:20,400
Three, two, one.

396
00:17:20,930 --> 00:17:21,680
Alright.

397
00:17:21,710 --> 00:17:22,690
Here, take a look.

398
00:17:22,690 --> 00:17:23,710
Thank you.

399
00:17:28,210 --> 00:17:30,000
Hello, Mom. I'm working right now.

400
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,060
What's the matter?

401
00:17:32,270 --> 00:17:34,130
Working overtime on the weekend?

402
00:17:34,930 --> 00:17:36,300
It's just an excuse.

403
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:38,400
Whenever she doesn't want
to answer the phone,

404
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,670
she is always busy.

405
00:17:41,150 --> 00:17:44,530
Miyu, I'm calling you for a reason.

406
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:48,160
We are family,
so I'll skip the pleasantries.

407
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:51,230
How much money do you
have left in your bank account?

408
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:52,790
Hello?

409
00:17:53,410 --> 00:17:54,540
Are you listening?

410
00:17:59,730 --> 00:18:00,620
Mom.

411
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:03,990
I still have to pay off
my debts every month.

412
00:18:03,990 --> 00:18:07,390
Ms. Xu, the Chinese restaurant's kitchen
is looking for you.

413
00:18:07,870 --> 00:18:09,400
Got it. I'll be right there.

414
00:18:09,890 --> 00:18:10,750
Mom, I have work to do.

415
00:18:10,750 --> 00:18:11,810
I'm hanging up now.

416
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:18,180
Hello?

417
00:18:23,450 --> 00:18:24,550
She is busy.

418
00:18:24,570 --> 00:18:25,230
She hung up.

419
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:28,360
Dad, what are you doing?

420
00:18:28,380 --> 00:18:29,380
Are you okay?

421
00:18:30,850 --> 00:18:31,850
See for yourself.

422
00:18:32,700 --> 00:18:34,070
In the past,

423
00:18:34,090 --> 00:18:35,120
even if you gave her
all the courage in the world,

424
00:18:35,120 --> 00:18:36,360
she wouldn't dare.

425
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:37,790
Now look at her.

426
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:39,550
Staying in a big city,

427
00:18:39,570 --> 00:18:40,920
living in a grand hotel.

428
00:18:40,950 --> 00:18:42,440
Now that she's divorced,

429
00:18:42,700 --> 00:18:44,900
she's doing great.

430
00:18:44,930 --> 00:18:45,820
What about us?

431
00:18:47,220 --> 00:18:49,250
We didn't get anything at all.

432
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:50,980
We're the ones losing out.

433
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:55,150
Xiumei.

434
00:18:55,380 --> 00:18:57,390
If she hangs up, call again.

435
00:18:57,410 --> 00:18:58,300
Keep calling.

436
00:18:58,330 --> 00:19:00,090
Call until she answers.

437
00:19:00,110 --> 00:19:00,910
Okay.

438
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:03,400
And you.

439
00:19:02,620 --> 00:19:03,160
[Call]

440
00:19:03,250 --> 00:19:04,150
[Miyu]

441
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:06,560
You don't even know your own limits.

442
00:19:06,980 --> 00:19:09,440
Why did you enroll Man
in an international school?

443
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:11,200
Why are you scolding me?

444
00:19:11,540 --> 00:19:14,470
Which parent doesn't
do everything for their child?

445
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:23,400
Hello, Mom.

446
00:19:23,590 --> 00:19:24,630
Miyu,

447
00:19:24,650 --> 00:19:26,450
you finally answered the phone.

448
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:29,200
I really couldn't go on otherwise.

449
00:19:29,830 --> 00:19:32,060
Mom, my life isn't easy either.

450
00:19:32,080 --> 00:19:33,090
I understand you,

451
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:35,630
but I'm fighting all alone in Shanghai.

452
00:19:36,070 --> 00:19:38,360
Have you ever asked me how I'm doing?

453
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:40,650
I really have no choice.

454
00:19:42,530 --> 00:19:44,030
Mom, I have no choice either.

455
00:19:44,030 --> 00:19:45,100
I can't help you.

456
00:19:45,620 --> 00:19:46,510
I'm sorry.

457
00:19:52,310 --> 00:19:53,910
Did something happen to you?

458
00:19:54,710 --> 00:19:56,250
No. You're looking for me?

459
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:58,920
Let's go.

460
00:20:20,530 --> 00:20:21,530
Let me make a corn.

461
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:00,160
Have a taste.

462
00:21:01,080 --> 00:21:04,010
You've learned to make
Suzhou-style boat pastries?

463
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:05,980
I didn't learn it systematically.

464
00:21:05,980 --> 00:21:08,060
I just picked it up from watching.

465
00:21:08,820 --> 00:21:10,820
They're just okay for a casual bite.

466
00:21:11,200 --> 00:21:12,660
Who taught you?

467
00:21:12,690 --> 00:21:13,990
My mom taught me.

468
00:21:14,560 --> 00:21:16,890
She only taught me
to make these few types.

469
00:21:17,160 --> 00:21:20,290
You mean your mom knows more?

470
00:21:20,330 --> 00:21:21,240
Yes.

471
00:21:21,780 --> 00:21:22,980
When my mom was young,

472
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:25,170
she learned from a master in town.

473
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,400
Every Chinese New Year, she also

474
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:28,530
makes some in different shapes for us.

475
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:31,210
She can even make Chinese zodiac animals.

476
00:21:34,150 --> 00:21:35,240
How about this?

477
00:21:35,350 --> 00:21:37,270
We'd like to invite your mother

478
00:21:37,270 --> 00:21:38,810
to come to Purong Hotel.

479
00:21:39,700 --> 00:21:40,880
We just want to observe

480
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:42,070
her boat pastries craftsmanship.

481
00:21:42,070 --> 00:21:43,160
There's no pressure.

482
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:44,880
We just want her to come over

483
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:45,640
and talk it through with us.

484
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,810
If there's really
an opportunity for cooperation,

485
00:21:47,810 --> 00:21:50,000
we'd be happy to see it happen.

486
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:00,720
If I had any other way,

487
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:02,640
I wouldn't come begging you.

488
00:22:01,660 --> 00:22:05,940
[Staff Only]

489
00:22:02,940 --> 00:22:06,030
Your sister is rummaging
through the house right now.

490
00:22:07,130 --> 00:22:08,430
Mom, do you still want the money?

491
00:22:08,430 --> 00:22:10,320
Yes, of course I do.

492
00:22:10,550 --> 00:22:11,350
Do you have it?

493
00:22:11,440 --> 00:22:13,760
If you want the money,
come here right now.

494
00:22:13,760 --> 00:22:17,560
[Staff Only]

495
00:22:19,190 --> 00:22:21,110
Your sister just finished tormenting you.

496
00:22:21,110 --> 00:22:23,000
Now you've brought your mom here.

497
00:22:23,030 --> 00:22:26,230
You really don't mind
the trouble your family brings you.

498
00:22:26,290 --> 00:22:28,120
Actually, I was quite hesitant at first.

499
00:22:28,120 --> 00:22:29,320
But then I thought,

500
00:22:29,340 --> 00:22:31,500
instead of having them
wait for me to feed them every day,

501
00:22:31,500 --> 00:22:33,870
it's better to let them
find their own way out.

502
00:22:33,870 --> 00:22:35,550
Actually, my mom's skills

503
00:22:35,570 --> 00:22:36,960
are really quite amazing.

504
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:39,500
It's just that she didn't have
a chance to show them off before.

505
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:41,130
The hotel happens to need it this time,

506
00:22:41,130 --> 00:22:42,590
so I wanted to give her a chance

507
00:22:42,590 --> 00:22:45,080
to discover her own value.

508
00:22:45,190 --> 00:22:46,520
She shouldn't always entrust her life

509
00:22:46,520 --> 00:22:47,850
to someone else.

510
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:49,850
That's a really nice thought.

511
00:22:49,870 --> 00:22:51,410
But knowing your mom's personality,

512
00:22:51,410 --> 00:22:52,520
once she's here,

513
00:22:52,550 --> 00:22:53,640
you won't be able to control her at all.

514
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:55,630
She'll cause trouble
for you all over the hotel.

515
00:22:55,630 --> 00:22:57,130
It absolutely won't happen this time.

516
00:22:57,130 --> 00:22:58,800
I've already laid down the rules with her.

517
00:22:58,800 --> 00:23:00,290
The hotel has its rules.

518
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:03,640
If she can't accept them,
she'll have to leave immediately.

519
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:06,250
Did you really say that?

520
00:23:07,070 --> 00:23:08,880
Not bad, Xu Miyu.

521
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,200
You're getting tough now.

522
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:12,460
With you backing me up,
who am I afraid of?

523
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:13,240
Let's go.

524
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:13,830
Let's go.

525
00:23:19,030 --> 00:23:19,770
Mr. Ji.

526
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:22,110
I have something else to do.

527
00:23:22,110 --> 00:23:23,160
I'll get going.

528
00:23:23,660 --> 00:23:24,590
Qiaoqi.

529
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:31,450
The desserts you made

530
00:23:31,590 --> 00:23:33,990
are not only beautiful but also delicious.

531
00:23:34,170 --> 00:23:35,170
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

532
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,970
About what happened last time,

533
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:41,400
I misunderstood you.

534
00:23:41,550 --> 00:23:44,280
And I said those nonsensical things.

535
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:45,470
What things?

536
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:49,690
Like whether you are worth it or not.

537
00:23:54,710 --> 00:23:57,270
I shouldn't meddle
in your private affairs.

538
00:23:57,310 --> 00:23:58,590
Whether it's worth it or not

539
00:23:58,590 --> 00:24:00,210
is not my place to judge.

540
00:24:01,050 --> 00:24:02,780
So I apologize to you.

541
00:24:03,110 --> 00:24:03,790
I'm sorry.

542
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:08,400
You don't need to apologize, Mr. Ji.

543
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:09,850
You have your standpoint,

544
00:24:09,850 --> 00:24:12,110
and I also did something inappropriate.

545
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:13,790
If there's nothing else,

546
00:24:14,140 --> 00:24:15,100
I'll get going.

547
00:24:15,360 --> 00:24:16,010
Miyu.

548
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:19,640
Are you still angry with me?

549
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:20,310
Yes.

550
00:24:20,490 --> 00:24:21,590
I am angry.

551
00:24:22,210 --> 00:24:24,090
I do not want to be the kind of person

552
00:24:24,090 --> 00:24:25,640
who forgives the moment
someone says sorry.

553
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:26,440
Is that okay?

554
00:24:27,750 --> 00:24:28,510
It is.

555
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:30,170
Of course it is.

556
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:02,500
Isn't this Chef Li?

557
00:25:02,530 --> 00:25:04,090
Why are you getting off work so late?

558
00:25:04,090 --> 00:25:06,290
Where did you go to save the world again?

559
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:08,350
Mr. Duan Jr.,
with you not at the hotel today,

560
00:25:08,350 --> 00:25:10,700
the world feels unusually peaceful.

561
00:25:14,260 --> 00:25:16,380
Do you know how to talk properly?

562
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:23,640
I heard Mr. Ji

563
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:27,040
has been thinking about
improving the afternoon tea lately.

564
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:29,640
The stuff your restaurant makes

565
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:31,370
is even more choking than dirt.

566
00:25:31,750 --> 00:25:32,830
Give it up.

567
00:25:33,410 --> 00:25:35,150
You've already turned
the Chinese restaurant around.

568
00:25:35,150 --> 00:25:37,550
Don't end up dragging
the Western one down.

569
00:25:37,770 --> 00:25:39,450
Don't you worry about that.

570
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:41,780
Mr. Ji has his secret weapon.

571
00:25:41,840 --> 00:25:43,370
What secret weapon?

572
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:44,920
No comment.

573
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:49,160
Is it that hard to admit defeat?

574
00:25:50,690 --> 00:25:52,550
What do you say? Care to make a bet?

575
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:54,530
Within a month,

576
00:25:54,550 --> 00:25:55,880
Purong's afternoon tea

577
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:57,190
will definitely be a big hit.

578
00:25:57,190 --> 00:25:59,990
The loser will be
the winner's sidekick for a week.

579
00:26:01,810 --> 00:26:02,850
You said it.

580
00:26:23,350 --> 00:26:23,960
Handsome.

581
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:24,790
Come here.

582
00:26:24,790 --> 00:26:25,640
Can you take a look?

583
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:27,920
Why can't I pay with WeChat?

584
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:29,130
Take a look.

585
00:26:29,310 --> 00:26:31,640
Ma'am, you haven't linked your bank card.

586
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:33,070
I haven't linked my bank card?

587
00:26:33,070 --> 00:26:34,070
Right, that's it.

588
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:36,570
Then could you pay for me?

589
00:26:37,040 --> 00:26:38,070
-I…
-I heard that

590
00:26:38,070 --> 00:26:39,680
your five-star hotel

591
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:41,310
puts the guest first.

592
00:26:41,310 --> 00:26:42,830
Guest comes first, right?

593
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:44,070
Sorry. I'll do it.

594
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:45,670
I'll do it.

595
00:26:46,910 --> 00:26:48,240
-Hello.
-I can’t pay.

596
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:50,110
Thank you.

597
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:52,550
Sweetie.

598
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:53,880
Give me a hug.

599
00:26:55,040 --> 00:26:56,260
Take a look.

600
00:26:57,160 --> 00:26:58,240
Do I look imposing?

601
00:26:58,440 --> 00:27:00,260
I almost didn't recognize you.

602
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:02,610
Your sister picked it for me.

603
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:04,160
After all, she's

604
00:27:04,180 --> 00:27:05,210
been around in the big city.

605
00:27:05,210 --> 00:27:05,850
Right?

606
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:06,880
Let me tell you,

607
00:27:06,880 --> 00:27:09,200
I've done my homework this time.

608
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:10,440
I won't let you down.

609
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:11,350
Okay. Let's go.

610
00:27:11,350 --> 00:27:11,920
Let's go.

611
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:25,590
Slow down. Wait.

612
00:27:25,590 --> 00:27:27,640
You're taking the food away too fast.

613
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,010
Just now, at the seafood section,

614
00:27:29,010 --> 00:27:31,640
I almost didn't get the sashimi.

615
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:32,970
I'm sorry, Ma'am.

616
00:27:34,500 --> 00:27:35,270
Look,

617
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:36,200
there's still so much left.

618
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:37,110
It's a waste not to eat it.

619
00:27:37,110 --> 00:27:38,160
Miss,

620
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,830
could you please help me put this

621
00:27:39,830 --> 00:27:40,960
on that table? That table over there.

622
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:41,640
Okay.

623
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:42,540
Okay.

624
00:27:43,310 --> 00:27:44,240
I'll hurry up and get some more.

625
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:46,500
Otherwise you guys will take it all away.

626
00:28:02,730 --> 00:28:04,580
Have you checked her background clearly?

627
00:28:04,580 --> 00:28:06,550
So far, we only know
she's Xu Miyu's mother,

628
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:07,610
named Jiao Xiumei.

629
00:28:07,610 --> 00:28:09,600
She used to farm in the countryside,

630
00:28:09,600 --> 00:28:11,480
and later opened
a guesthouse with her husband,

631
00:28:11,480 --> 00:28:13,410
but the business wasn't very good.

632
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:20,170
Waiter!

633
00:28:20,810 --> 00:28:21,410
Waiter!

634
00:28:21,770 --> 00:28:22,770
Why is no one here?

635
00:28:23,620 --> 00:28:24,780
I know.

636
00:28:26,190 --> 00:28:27,180
Hold on, please.

637
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:28,980
Espresso?

638
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:33,160
Okay.

639
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:36,270
Keep going.

640
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:37,350
I can hear you guys.

641
00:28:41,150 --> 00:28:44,660
I want to know about
the representative pieces.

642
00:28:45,010 --> 00:28:45,650
Yeah.

643
00:28:54,540 --> 00:28:56,560
Very impressive.

644
00:29:12,030 --> 00:29:12,830
Why

645
00:29:13,670 --> 00:29:15,670
is it as bitter as Chinese medicine?

646
00:29:18,110 --> 00:29:19,240
This Ji Feng...

647
00:29:19,720 --> 00:29:20,830
Bringing a village woman

648
00:29:20,830 --> 00:29:23,230
to save afternoon tea
at a five-star hotel,

649
00:29:24,550 --> 00:29:26,810
is he taking an unconventional approach

650
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:28,250
or is he out of options?

651
00:29:28,550 --> 00:29:30,160
I guess he has no way out.

652
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:31,880
After all, we've given a heads-up

653
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,180
to all the dessert businesses in the city.

654
00:29:33,180 --> 00:29:35,380
It's not that easy to hire a master chef.

655
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:38,210
I hope so.

656
00:29:41,030 --> 00:29:43,680
We will work with local artists.

657
00:29:43,710 --> 00:29:47,570
But we also want to
expand into international markets.

658
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:48,290
Yeah.

659
00:29:49,230 --> 00:29:50,400
Besides...

660
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:01,590
Mom.

661
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:03,530
You took so much food.

662
00:30:03,560 --> 00:30:04,880
Can you finish it?

663
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:06,480
I can.

664
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:09,700
I was in a hurry last time
I came to see you.

665
00:30:10,020 --> 00:30:12,060
Today I'm going to eat as much as I want.

666
00:30:12,060 --> 00:30:13,340
Then eat quickly.

667
00:30:13,370 --> 00:30:14,350
You have to come with me later.

668
00:30:14,350 --> 00:30:15,640
Many people in the kitchen
are waiting for you.

669
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:16,960
Don't rush me.

670
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,110
Morning, Ms. Xu.

671
00:30:19,840 --> 00:30:21,500
-Morning, Mr. Tan.
-Morning.

672
00:30:23,110 --> 00:30:23,880
This is...

673
00:30:24,110 --> 00:30:26,100
This, this is my mother.

674
00:30:26,130 --> 00:30:27,880
This is our guest, Mr. Tan.

675
00:30:27,970 --> 00:30:29,170
Hello, Mrs. Xu.

676
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:31,610
So you can speak Chinese.

677
00:30:32,110 --> 00:30:34,510
He was the one
who poured me coffee just now.

678
00:30:34,550 --> 00:30:36,210
I heard him speaking English.

679
00:30:36,210 --> 00:30:37,720
I haven't had the chance to thank you yet.

680
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:38,240
Thank you.

681
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,590
It's nothing.

682
00:30:39,740 --> 00:30:40,400
Thank you, Mr. Tan.

683
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:41,330
You're welcome.

684
00:30:41,350 --> 00:30:42,590
Well, take your time.

685
00:30:42,590 --> 00:30:43,450
I'll get going.

686
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,240
I'm done eating too.

687
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:46,310
Let's go together.

688
00:30:46,930 --> 00:30:47,770
It's fine.

689
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:49,810
What do you mean, go together?

690
00:30:50,380 --> 00:30:51,400
He's a guest.

691
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:53,070
Don't try to get close to him.

692
00:30:53,100 --> 00:30:55,510
Don't think I don't know who Mr. Tan is.

693
00:30:55,710 --> 00:30:57,510
Your sister told me everything.

694
00:30:58,770 --> 00:31:00,070
Tell me the truth.

695
00:31:00,350 --> 00:31:01,960
How far have you two gone?

696
00:31:01,960 --> 00:31:02,880
Nowhere.

697
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:05,440
I think he's pretty good.

698
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:06,680
He is good-looking,

699
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:08,060
and capable.

700
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:09,360
And he's good to you.

701
00:31:09,830 --> 00:31:11,030
Don't be so indifferent.

702
00:31:11,030 --> 00:31:12,550
Give him a chance.

703
00:31:12,550 --> 00:31:13,660
Mom.

704
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,920
Let me say this to you again.

705
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:16,080
This is a hotel.

706
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:17,650
I'm here to work and make money,

707
00:31:17,650 --> 00:31:19,280
and the guests
aren't here for blind dates.

708
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:20,750
Stop trying to play matchmaker,

709
00:31:20,750 --> 00:31:21,310
okay?

710
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:22,910
Don't play innocent with me.

711
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:24,720
I'm doing this for your own good.

712
00:31:24,740 --> 00:31:26,350
You're in your thirties.

713
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:28,030
Aren't you going to find a partner?

714
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:29,070
Without a family,

715
00:31:29,070 --> 00:31:31,550
who's going to be
with you when you're old?

716
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:32,960
Think clearly about it.

717
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:34,890
Mom, stop meddling in my business.

718
00:31:35,050 --> 00:31:36,790
There are people upstairs
waiting to assess you.

719
00:31:36,790 --> 00:31:38,450
Mind your own business first.

720
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:41,510
Let's just live our own lives, okay?

721
00:31:41,510 --> 00:31:42,490
Fine.

722
00:31:42,610 --> 00:31:44,070
You're all grown up now,

723
00:31:44,100 --> 00:31:46,030
and you don't listen to me anymore.

724
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:47,850
Let's get going.

725
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:53,880
Chef Jiao will be here soon.

726
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,740
So we need to hurry up.

727
00:31:57,860 --> 00:31:58,660
That'll do.

728
00:32:00,550 --> 00:32:01,390
Mr. Ji.

729
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:02,960
Why are you here?

730
00:32:02,990 --> 00:32:04,160
Chef Jiao is visiting.

731
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:06,160
Of course I have to
welcome her personally.

732
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:07,240
Pleased to meet you.

733
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:08,970
So you are the general manager?

734
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:11,990
I've often heard Miyu talk about you.

735
00:32:12,010 --> 00:32:14,420
Look at this temperament and appearance.

736
00:32:15,070 --> 00:32:17,260
You're better than the stars on TV.

737
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,440
General Manager.

738
00:32:18,590 --> 00:32:19,790
Are you married?

739
00:32:19,810 --> 00:32:21,680
Mom, what are you saying?

740
00:32:23,050 --> 00:32:23,920
It's okay.

741
00:32:24,740 --> 00:32:25,740
I'm still single.

742
00:32:29,290 --> 00:32:31,200
Then let's begin.

743
00:32:31,250 --> 00:32:32,600
Okay.

744
00:32:32,630 --> 00:32:33,690
I've prepared it for you.

745
00:32:33,690 --> 00:32:34,490
Okay.

746
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,840
We have prepared some tools for you.

747
00:32:42,840 --> 00:32:44,570
See if they are suitable.

748
00:32:44,770 --> 00:32:47,480
Things in a big hotel
are truly professional.

749
00:32:47,510 --> 00:32:48,530
Then I'll use them.

750
00:32:48,530 --> 00:32:49,270
Okay.

751
00:34:23,980 --> 00:34:25,540
Blooming Prosperity.

752
00:34:26,580 --> 00:34:28,110
Abundance Year After Year.

753
00:34:28,860 --> 00:34:31,170
Look, this keeps the flowers fresh.

754
00:34:31,199 --> 00:34:31,900
Look.

755
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:33,179
Right? So fresh.

756
00:34:37,540 --> 00:34:38,139
Mom,

757
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:39,909
is your arthritis acting up again?

758
00:34:39,909 --> 00:34:41,840
It's nothing. Just an old problem.

759
00:34:51,179 --> 00:34:52,580
Come, Chef Jiao, please.

760
00:34:58,930 --> 00:35:00,930
This room faces south.

761
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:05,960
Do I have to pay for this room?

762
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:08,190
Chef Jiao, you are
the boat pastry consultant

763
00:35:08,190 --> 00:35:09,070
for our hotel.

764
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:11,190
All food and accommodation expenses

765
00:35:11,190 --> 00:35:12,550
will be covered by us.

766
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:13,320
You don't need to worry.

767
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,140
Then,

768
00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:16,110
if I eat and stay here,

769
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:17,840
will I still get paid?

770
00:35:17,930 --> 00:35:20,760
Mom, let's talk about the contract later.

771
00:35:20,780 --> 00:35:22,250
We can talk about the contract later,

772
00:35:22,250 --> 00:35:23,910
but we must be clear about the money.

773
00:35:23,910 --> 00:35:25,180
Your dad told me

774
00:35:25,210 --> 00:35:27,470
to ask about the money clearly in person.

775
00:35:27,510 --> 00:35:28,670
If the pay isn't clear,

776
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:30,190
I can't start working.

777
00:35:30,190 --> 00:35:30,710
Right?

778
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:31,670
Yes, it's fine.

779
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:34,400
What is your ideal salary, Chef Jiao?

780
00:35:36,630 --> 00:35:38,150
7,000 a month.

781
00:35:38,170 --> 00:35:39,970
That's not too much, right?

782
00:35:40,230 --> 00:35:40,910
No problem.

783
00:35:40,930 --> 00:35:41,520
Okay.

784
00:35:41,650 --> 00:35:42,250
No.

785
00:35:42,270 --> 00:35:44,680
7,000 is too little.

786
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:46,370
Mom, we'll discuss this later.

787
00:35:46,370 --> 00:35:47,370
8,000.

788
00:35:47,390 --> 00:35:49,850
At least 8,500.

789
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:52,590
Chef Jiao, you don't
need to answer me right away.

790
00:35:52,590 --> 00:35:54,790
We can talk when you've thought it over.

791
00:35:58,110 --> 00:35:58,920
Ms. Xu,

792
00:35:59,290 --> 00:36:00,350
please take care of

793
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,760
Chef Jiao's daily needs.

794
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:04,280
We hope Chef Jiao
can start working immediately.

795
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:06,760
We will also draft the contract
as soon as possible.

796
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:07,590
When the time comes, please

797
00:36:07,590 --> 00:36:09,040
help Chef Jiao review it.

798
00:36:09,190 --> 00:36:10,550
Okay, Mr. Ji. Thank you.

799
00:36:11,730 --> 00:36:12,400
Right.

800
00:36:12,430 --> 00:36:14,060
Um, here is the room card.

801
00:36:24,490 --> 00:36:25,300
Get some rest.

802
00:36:34,600 --> 00:36:35,440
Mom.

803
00:36:36,070 --> 00:36:37,130
Congratulations.

804
00:36:38,860 --> 00:36:39,650
So?

805
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,590
I'm quite capable, am I?

806
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:42,800
Of course.

807
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:45,150
Let's eat some fruit.

808
00:36:45,190 --> 00:36:47,080
Look how fresh it is.

809
00:36:47,360 --> 00:36:49,320
As expected of a five-star hotel.

810
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,510
Here, let me wipe it for you.

811
00:36:49,640 --> 00:36:51,050
[Yunnan Baiyao Plaster]

812
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:52,370
[Yunnan Baiyao Plaster]

813
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:02,000
Rui,

814
00:37:02,630 --> 00:37:04,030
can Chef Jiao's contract

815
00:37:04,030 --> 00:37:05,320
be ready this week?

816
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:09,320
There are a bunch of contracts lined up.

817
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:11,630
First come, first served, okay?

818
00:37:11,670 --> 00:37:13,800
The afternoon tea project is urgent.

819
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:15,060
Please prioritize it.

820
00:37:19,850 --> 00:37:22,760
It seems that what's urgent,
aside from afternoon tea,

821
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:23,960
is someone's eagerness

822
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:26,320
to show goodwill with an ulterior motive.

823
00:37:26,630 --> 00:37:27,400
What?

824
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:29,400
Haven't apologized yet?

825
00:37:30,590 --> 00:37:31,190
I have.

826
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:33,960
Then that's it.

827
00:37:34,510 --> 00:37:35,910
But she didn't accept it.

828
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,550
Xu Miyu?

829
00:37:42,430 --> 00:37:43,890
Actually, I'm quite glad.

830
00:37:43,900 --> 00:37:44,930
She was willing to tell me

831
00:37:44,930 --> 00:37:46,860
that she didn't accept my apology.

832
00:37:49,320 --> 00:37:50,550
Glad?

833
00:37:51,760 --> 00:37:54,760
Telling the truth
is always better than holding it in.

834
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:58,000
This way, I know what I should do.

835
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:03,280
Feng,

836
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:04,920
are you okay?

837
00:38:06,070 --> 00:38:07,150
The contract.

838
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:09,370
Remember to give it to me this week.

839
00:38:10,010 --> 00:38:10,860
Okay.

840
00:38:16,170 --> 00:38:16,790
[Statement Regarding the Reception
of VIP Guest Mr. Ma Wenhui]

841
00:38:16,820 --> 00:38:17,430
[During my reception of Mr. Ma Wenhui,]

842
00:38:17,450 --> 00:38:18,040
[my attitude caused him
an unpleasant experience.]

843
00:38:18,060 --> 00:38:18,560
[I hereby submit this statement.]

844
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:19,310
[Submitted by Lu Xiaoyan]

845
00:38:25,440 --> 00:38:27,040
I understand the situation.

846
00:38:27,110 --> 00:38:27,670
Learn from this.

847
00:38:27,670 --> 00:38:29,130
Don't let it happen again.

848
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:32,000
Don't think I'm
scared of you because of this.

849
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:33,860
I don't need you to be scared of me.

850
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:38,480
These are the Western restaurant's
newly launched

851
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:39,830
afternoon tea boat pastries.

852
00:38:39,830 --> 00:38:41,420
You've all worked hard
these past couple of days.

853
00:38:41,420 --> 00:38:42,540
Try them.

854
00:38:55,740 --> 00:38:57,050
They look so nice.

855
00:38:57,080 --> 00:38:58,510
Then eat them yourself.

856
00:38:59,100 --> 00:39:00,360
Then I won't be polite.

857
00:39:02,140 --> 00:39:04,500
[Blooming Prosperity]

858
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:03,480
What is this?

859
00:39:03,480 --> 00:39:04,630
This is also our specialty.

860
00:39:04,530 --> 00:39:07,320
[Abundance Year After Year]

861
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:06,640
I'll take both then.

862
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:07,890
Sure, wait a moment.

863
00:39:27,050 --> 00:39:28,370
[Employment Contract]

864
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:31,830
[Work content] [Reward]

865
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:33,290
20,000? So high?

866
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:35,320
Mom, your boat pastries became a hit
in our Western restaurant

867
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:37,630
in just one afternoon.

868
00:39:37,670 --> 00:39:38,730
Really?

869
00:39:42,220 --> 00:39:43,320
I've never had so much money

870
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:45,760
in my pocket my whole life.

871
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:48,900
Now I see it clearly.

872
00:39:49,210 --> 00:39:50,830
That Mr. Ji

873
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:52,510
probably has his eye on you.

874
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:53,920
Mom, what nonsense are you talking about?

875
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:54,930
Otherwise,

876
00:39:54,950 --> 00:39:57,070
why would he pay an old lady like me

877
00:39:57,070 --> 00:39:58,510
such a high salary?

878
00:39:58,550 --> 00:40:00,190
It's called a consulting fee.

879
00:40:00,190 --> 00:40:01,320
Whatever fee it is,

880
00:40:01,340 --> 00:40:02,990
he is doing it to please you.

881
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:04,960
This is the result of a joint assessment

882
00:40:04,960 --> 00:40:05,710
by the HR Department,

883
00:40:05,710 --> 00:40:07,150
the Administration Department,

884
00:40:07,150 --> 00:40:08,800
and the Business Management Department.

885
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,260
It's not just his call.

886
00:40:10,290 --> 00:40:11,110
Besides,

887
00:40:11,110 --> 00:40:12,230
you should have some confidence

888
00:40:12,230 --> 00:40:13,630
in your own skills, okay?

889
00:40:14,550 --> 00:40:16,960
You are the one
who should have confidence.

890
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:18,880
When have I ever been wrong?

891
00:40:18,880 --> 00:40:20,880
The way he looks at you is different.

892
00:40:23,310 --> 00:40:24,590
Mr. Tan

893
00:40:24,620 --> 00:40:26,190
and Mr. Ji.

894
00:40:26,210 --> 00:40:27,810
Both seem like good catches.

895
00:40:27,940 --> 00:40:29,340
Which one do you like more?

896
00:40:29,340 --> 00:40:30,220
While I'm here,

897
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:31,730
I'll help you pull some strings.

898
00:40:31,730 --> 00:40:34,450
Mom, stop dreaming, will you?

899
00:40:35,080 --> 00:40:36,150
I understand your anxiety

900
00:40:36,150 --> 00:40:37,440
about having an older,

901
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:39,360
divorced daughter.

902
00:40:39,380 --> 00:40:40,410
But that's your problem.

903
00:40:40,410 --> 00:40:41,500
It has nothing to do with me.

904
00:40:41,500 --> 00:40:42,670
And it certainly has nothing to do

905
00:40:42,670 --> 00:40:44,320
with Mr. Tan and Mr. Ji.

906
00:40:44,340 --> 00:40:47,140
One is my guest,

907
00:40:47,170 --> 00:40:48,440
and making sure he's not disturbed

908
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:49,320
is my job.

909
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:51,630
The other is my boss.

910
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:53,630
He could easily get us both fired

911
00:40:53,630 --> 00:40:55,110
by lifting a finger.

912
00:40:55,130 --> 00:40:57,420
They are not from the same world as me.

913
00:40:57,450 --> 00:40:58,400
Do you understand?

914
00:40:58,400 --> 00:41:00,760
What... what are you talking about?

915
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:01,360
Alright, alright.

916
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:02,280
Just focus on work

917
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:03,570
right now.

918
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:06,450
There's no problem with the contract.
Just sign it.

919
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:08,240
So stubborn.

920
00:41:11,030 --> 00:41:12,030
Where do I sign?

921
00:41:23,070 --> 00:41:24,320
Duan,

922
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:25,780
hurry up.

923
00:41:25,930 --> 00:41:27,570
There are still pots to wash.

924
00:41:32,240 --> 00:41:33,400
The water's barely running.

925
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:34,930
How can you wash them clean?

926
00:41:38,850 --> 00:41:41,040
Li Qiaoqi, don't go too far.

927
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:44,570
Getting mad already?

928
00:41:45,180 --> 00:41:46,690
You made the bet yourself.

929
00:41:46,720 --> 00:41:48,120
You must accept the loss.

930
00:41:48,860 --> 00:41:50,120
You don't really think

931
00:41:50,150 --> 00:41:51,920
that just by improving the afternoon tea,

932
00:41:51,920 --> 00:41:53,570
Purong can turn the tables, do you?

933
00:41:53,570 --> 00:41:55,190
The best is yet to come.

934
00:42:05,550 --> 00:42:07,550
You did that on purpose, didn't you?

935
00:42:07,910 --> 00:42:09,770
Purong's dishes are too fragile.

936
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:10,570
Pay for it.

937
00:42:22,250 --> 00:42:24,180
It's not like I can't afford to pay.

938
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:39,130
The contract is signed. Thank you, Mr. Ji.

939
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:45,300
You don't need to thank me.

940
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:46,760
Your mother's willingness to entrust

941
00:42:46,760 --> 00:42:48,090
this craft to Purong Hotel

942
00:42:48,090 --> 00:42:49,380
is our fortune.

943
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,770
[You don't need to thank me.
Your mother's willingness to entrust]

944
00:42:53,790 --> 00:42:55,650
[this craft to Purong Hotel
is our fortune.]

945
00:43:03,120 --> 00:43:07,280
[Xu Miyu]

946
00:43:07,710 --> 00:43:09,440
If you must thank me,

947
00:43:10,670 --> 00:43:11,590
how about

948
00:43:12,710 --> 00:43:14,000
we have dinner together?
